<li>Analysis of upstream regions of the BaeSR regulon with the motif-ﬁnding program revealed an 18-bp consensus sequence , 5 - TTTTTC TCCATDATTGGC-3 ( where D is G , A , or T ) , and it revealed that this consensus sequence is required for gene induction by BaeR .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=15716448" target="_blank">15716448</a>]<br></li>
