<li>As in the case of spy promoter , both CpxR and BaeR bind to the promoters for two drug exporter genes , acrD and mdtA , but the BaeR-binding site on these promoters partially overlaps with the respective CpxR-binding site ( Hirakawa et al. , 2004 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=17884222" target="_blank">17884222</a>]<br></li>
